Package: uncertaintymeasures
Type: Package
Title: Functions to create uncertainty measures using turbulence
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Sebastian", "Stoeckl", email = "", role = c("aut","cre")))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Functions to replicate and create uncertainty measures using in-sample and out-of-ssample turbulence. Additionally the package provides the portfolio adjustment factors for the minimax rule under multiple priors according to Garlappi, Uppal & Wang (2008, RFS).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
