    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Imports: xts, mice, fAssets, zoo, timeSeries, nleqslv, plyr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/sstoeckl/uncertaintymeasures
BugReports: https://github.com/sstoeckl/uncertaintymeasures/issues
